text: The Regionalliga is the third level in Austrian association football. The Regionalliga is divided into 3 divisions. ==Regionalliga in Austria== *Regionalliga Ost:It covers the Austrian states of Burgenland, Lower Austria and Vienna. *Regionalliga Mitte:It is formed by teams from Upper Austria, Styria, Carinthia and East Tyrol. *Eliteliga (West):It is formed by teams from the federal states Vorarlberg, Tyrol (only North Tyrol) and Salzburg. ===History=== In the 1959-60 Regionalliga Ost and Mitte were formed, Regionalliga West a year later. Till 1973/74 the Regionalliga was the 2nd level in Austrian football. The champions were promoted to the highest league.
